# Runtime artifacts the orchestrator writes to a consumer repo. Not usually
# relevant inside the plugin repo itself (sensible-ralph isn't typically a
# ralph consumer of its own skills), but shipped so the list is easy to
# copy-paste from here if the plugin's own development ever involves a
# dispatch.
/.sensible-ralph/
/.worktrees/
/.sensible-ralph-base-sha
ralph-output.log

# Handoff files between close-issue (sensible-ralph plugin skill) and the
# project-local close-branch skill at .claude/skills/close-branch/. Written
# at the start of each close ritual and deleted at the end; presence between
# runs means the previous /close-issue was interrupted.
/.close-branch-inputs
/.close-branch-result
